name: Pretty Fly
description:
Those who don’t jump will never fly.
Pretty Fly is a Pretty Simple concept,
quite literally. It’s about letting go of
your fear of the unknown. Letting go
of anticipation and embrace the
moment. Grounding yourself in the
weightlessness feeling of adrenaline
while seizing the chance to be
surprised by the destination you’ll
reach. Collaboration mbsjq x
maalavidaa
